    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed and all achieved their required gradation levels under MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed; the team's narrative position is that the factor does not apply to a sensitivity-ranking COU with a fixed operating envelope. The package is accepted on the basis of the twelve assessed factors satisfying MRL 3 requirements. The unassessed factor did not trigger a formal risk escalation review.",
